# 🎯 12. Interview Traps ⚠️

## ❓ Difference: `floor` vs `ceil`

| Function | Behavior |
| -------- | -------- |
| floor    | down     |
| ceil     | up       |

---

## ❓ Why not use `round` for random?

👉 Uneven probability

---

## ❓ `NaN` case

```js
Math.sqrt(-1) // NaN
```

---

# 🎯 13. Advanced Tricks 🔥

## 🔹 Clamp value between min & max

```js
function clamp(val, min, max) {
  return Math.min(Math.max(val, min), max);
}
```

---

## 🔹 Check if integer

```js
Number.isInteger(5) // true
```

---

## 🔹 Convert degrees → radians

```js
deg * (Math.PI / 180)
```

